tyle="font-size: 70.7%; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">α</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> , and then connect the pairs between which there were observed phase transitions in SGD. In doing this we repeatedly observe this same pattern: structure seems to form in particular ways, consistently decreasing loss while increasing complexity. Some transitions are dynamically permissible, and others aren&#39;t.</p><p> This single plot of loss against complexity captures the growth and form of TMS. </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:74.65%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/lsqupunlqrjpkblefvgx" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/tys7ftwbiizkvzybhktd 210w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/zcriwtr2akqrm2adnu8f 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/ar3nffhvteibhxwxyylu 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/bqcgvdg5seifbpugiilk 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/moeo6nf0pmypueoimcp2 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/q9sqwotqljejhhn9ssik 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/ryrz7q27gxfuktxl9a2e 1470w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/jvGqQGDrYzZM4MyaN/svdokmrwnqgnsxrywesc 1680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lessw